Hi - Does anyone know why when I try to convert an old DND page to a DND area that the template just donesn't appear in the list to select from?

If I change the template back to a flex column, it appears.. just not as a DND area.

Appears with this
```  {% widget_container "my_flexible_column" label="Main body content" %}
  {% end_widget_container %}```
Doesn't appear with
```{% dnd_area "body_dnd_area" %}
	&lt;!-- generates an empty drag and drop area drop-section --&gt;
{% end_dnd_area %}```
